# Shared Core Rules

Core modules must be framework-light where possible.

Allowed in src/core:
- TypeScript types
- constants
- pure functions
- deterministic calculations
- report builders
- AI helper wrappers
- project helpers

Avoid in src/core:
- React components
- page routing
- direct DOM usage
- UI styling
- component state
- localStorage unless isolated behind a service

Core should be reusable later by:
- Refurb Genius
- Deal Copilot
- Refurb IQ

Pricing, ROI, and report logic must be importable from core.
